<h2>About Nimap Infotech Task</h2>

<p>
    <strong>Project Overview:</strong>
    Nimap Infotech Task is a web application designed to demonstrate full-stack development skills
    using ASP.NET MVC with ADO.NET. The project includes basic CRUD operations for managing categories and products,
    implementing pagination and data handling for smooth user interaction.
</p>

<p>
    <strong>Features:</strong>
    <ul>
        <li>CRUD operations for categories and products.</li>
        <li>Display product and category data with pagination.</li>
        <li>Data handling using ADO.NET.</li>
        <li>Responsive user interface using Bootstrap and simple HTML forms.</li>
    </ul>
</p>

<p>
    <strong>Technology Stack:</strong>
    <ul>
        <li>Backend: ASP.NET MVC</li>
        <li>Frontend: HTML, CSS, JavaScript, Bootstrap</li>
        <li>Database Access: ADO.NET</li>
        <li>Database: SQL Server</li>
    </ul>
</p>

<p>
    <strong>Purpose of the Project:</strong>
    This project is developed to showcase the integration of front-end and back-end technologies in a real-world scenario.
    It demonstrates the ability to handle data using ADO.NET, implement business logic, and create user-friendly interfaces.
</p>




